```{r}
source("analysis.R")
gci = filter(rbind(read.al(paste("./input-entries/", "gci", 1, ".csv", sep=""))), status == 200)
nogci = filter(rbind(read.al(paste("./input-entries/", "nogci", 1, ".csv", sep=""))), status == 200)
print_latency_summary_table(nogci, gci, "NOGCI", "GCI  ")
plot_ecdf(gci,nogci, 150)
```

```{r}
gci = filter(rbind(read.al(paste("./local-debug-input/", "gci", 1, ".csv", sep=""))), status == 200)

stats(gci$latency,     paste("gci-latency    ", sep=""))
```
